description: Removes an object associated with a profile of a given ProfileObjectType.

parameters.name: ProfileId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of a customer profile.

parameters.name: ProfileObjectUniqueKey
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the profile object generated by the service.

parameters.name: ObjectTypeName
parameters.description: The name of the profile object type.

parameters.name: DomainName
parameters.description: The unique name of the domain.

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: A message that indicates the delete request is done.
